fr.epita.sp18.entity

Class Identity

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.epita.sp18.entity.Identity

  • public class Identity
extends java.lang.Object
    Define the Identity class, that keep all identity's information of the IAM-Project. The Identity properties are:

    Long uid - Primary key of the identity

    String name - Display name of the identity

    String email - Email of the identity. Unique value, used for authentication service

    String normalizedEmail - Email of the identity in upper case. Unique value, used for searching the identity by email

    String passwordHash - Password of the identity, encode by BCryptPasswordEncoder

    Author:
    Philip
